1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,670 --> 00:01:40,960
[Her Fantastic Adventures]

3
00:01:48,060 --> 00:01:48,780
It's you.

4
00:01:48,810 --> 00:01:49,740
You're here too.

5
00:01:50,220 --> 00:01:50,940
I swear

6
00:01:51,080 --> 00:01:52,700
I'm not Lu Zizheng,

7
00:01:52,740 --> 00:01:53,770
What is this?

8
00:01:54,009 --> 00:01:55,289
You consider me a friend?

9
00:01:55,289 --> 00:01:57,470
Haven't you realized who I am?

10
00:01:57,590 --> 00:01:58,330
It's me.

11
00:01:58,360 --> 00:01:59,440
You big fool.

12
00:01:59,490 --> 00:02:01,420
Since Lu Zizheng is so important to you,

13
00:02:01,420 --> 00:02:03,060
just call me Lu Zizheng.

14
00:02:03,080 --> 00:02:04,310
Because you saved my life,

15
00:02:04,310 --> 00:02:05,880
your life

16
00:02:06,010 --> 00:02:09,210
is very, very, very important to me.

17
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:10,750
Let's make up.

18
00:02:10,850 --> 00:02:12,650
I don't want to fall out with you

19
00:02:12,670 --> 00:02:14,070
over these messy things.

20
00:02:15,010 --> 00:02:16,490
Remember to return it to me.

21
00:02:16,490 --> 00:02:18,490
Do you also think I'm unforgivable?

22
00:02:18,490 --> 00:02:20,490
I'm not the Lu Zizheng you think I am.

23
00:02:21,050 --> 00:02:22,010
Take care.

24
00:02:22,440 --> 00:02:25,780
[Xiling Sect]

25
00:02:30,810 --> 00:02:32,290
Lu Zizheng!

26
00:02:32,290 --> 00:02:34,360
Lu Zizheng!

27
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:36,970
Lu Zizheng!

28
00:02:42,010 --> 00:02:43,800
Where have you gone?

29
00:02:45,510 --> 00:02:47,960
[Episode 21]

30
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,160
Lu Zi...

31
00:03:02,980 --> 00:03:05,770
[Xiling Sect]

32
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,280
Lu Zizheng?

33
00:03:07,490 --> 00:03:09,220
Do you really not want to see me?

34
00:03:10,410 --> 00:03:11,770
Better a quick death than prolonged pain.

35
00:03:11,770 --> 00:03:13,100
This time must have been

36
00:03:14,010 --> 00:03:15,180
very hard for you.

37
00:03:16,420 --> 00:03:17,350
Not for my heart.

38
00:03:18,050 --> 00:03:18,920
But it is for my life.

39
00:03:18,920 --> 00:03:20,500
Then why did you join Xiling?

40
00:03:20,500 --> 00:03:21,750
That's my personal business.

41
00:03:21,750 --> 00:03:25,310
[Xiling Sect]

42
00:03:22,090 --> 00:03:22,730
Qiao.

43
00:03:24,290 --> 00:03:25,370
Is the poison you were affected with before

44
00:03:25,370 --> 00:03:26,250
gone now?

45
00:03:26,530 --> 00:03:28,250
My heart is already poisoned to death,

46
00:03:28,250 --> 00:03:29,130
so I'm cured.

47
00:03:30,130 --> 00:03:31,490
The one who's poisonous is you.

48
00:03:31,490 --> 00:03:32,490
I'm not poisoned.

49
00:03:32,530 --> 00:03:33,790
You don't have poison,

50
00:03:33,850 --> 00:03:35,170
and you can't be poisoned,

51
00:03:35,170 --> 00:03:36,700
because you are the poison.

52
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,650
The kind that kills if touched.

53
00:03:40,130 --> 00:03:41,610
At that time, I didn't want to kill you.

54
00:03:41,610 --> 00:03:43,010
I just wanted to save you.

55
00:03:46,100 --> 00:03:47,100
Do you believe me?

56
00:03:47,130 --> 00:03:48,050
Of course not.

57
00:03:54,770 --> 00:03:55,570
Xing Si,

58
00:03:56,730 --> 00:03:58,050
she hates me

59
00:03:59,210 --> 00:04:00,410
more than I imagined.

60
00:04:01,130 --> 00:04:01,890
Young Master,

61
00:04:01,890 --> 00:04:03,730
we can't keep going like this.

62
00:04:03,920 --> 00:04:05,520
We need to come up with a plan.

63
00:04:06,340 --> 00:04:08,140
You want me to come up with a plan?

64
00:04:09,100 --> 00:04:10,930
You're a writer of romance novels

65
00:04:10,930 --> 00:04:12,930
and you want me to come up with a plan?

66
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,680
Are you crazy?

67
00:04:14,930 --> 00:04:17,970
A writer of romance novels?

68
00:04:20,100 --> 00:04:22,360
That must be Gu Qingqiao's words, right?

69
00:04:22,890 --> 00:04:24,020
Who else could it be?

70
00:04:24,060 --> 00:04:25,090
Me?

71
00:04:25,330 --> 00:04:26,130
Young Master.

72
00:04:26,170 --> 00:04:27,080
Do you know

73
00:04:27,370 --> 00:04:29,370
that you've learned her bad habits?

74
00:04:29,410 --> 00:04:32,420
I think it doesn't matter if we take her back or not.

75
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:33,450
Yes.

76
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,850
What matters is

77
00:04:36,130 --> 00:04:37,820
whether we can get her out of here.

78
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:38,620
Young Master,

79
00:04:38,810 --> 00:04:41,220
there's another meaning in my words.

80
00:04:41,220 --> 00:04:42,010
Shut up.

81
00:04:42,409 --> 00:04:43,330
Also,

82
00:04:43,330 --> 00:04:45,190
we can't let Qiao and Ruan Siqiong

83
00:04:45,570 --> 00:04:46,650
stay together.

84
00:04:46,780 --> 00:04:47,680
Alright, alright.

85
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,450
You should go to bed.

86
00:04:48,450 --> 00:04:49,950
Ignore what I said, okay?

87
00:04:56,970 --> 00:04:57,770
Sky lanterns?

88
00:05:16,290 --> 00:05:17,550
I forgot to write on it!

89
00:05:22,940 --> 00:05:23,610
Qiao.

90
00:05:24,210 --> 00:05:25,070
Let me help you.

91
00:05:27,850 --> 00:05:28,450
Thank you.

92
00:05:28,930 --> 00:05:29,570
Qing.

93
00:05:30,010 --> 00:05:30,940
Do you need help?

94
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:34,700
Master Ruan, could you please hold the sky lantern for me?

95
00:05:36,010 --> 00:05:36,930
Predecessor Ruan.

96
00:05:36,930 --> 00:05:38,350
Qiao and I have unfinished business.

97
00:05:38,350 --> 00:05:40,390
Qing doesn't want to talk to you.

98
00:05:41,250 --> 00:05:43,170
There are some misunderstandings between us.

99
00:05:43,170 --> 00:05:44,770
I think it's because you have ulterior motives.

100
00:05:44,770 --> 00:05:46,050
We don't need outsiders

101
00:05:46,050 --> 00:05:48,050
to interfere in our matters.

102
00:05:59,650 --> 00:06:00,330
Duan Yu.

103
00:06:01,210 --> 00:06:02,730
Take my words seriously.

104
00:06:03,450 --> 00:06:05,130
I don't know anything about the Sacred Blood Sect,

105
00:06:05,130 --> 00:06:06,400
and I don't want to get involved in the issues between

106
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:08,210
the Sacred Blood Sect and the Duan family.

107
00:06:08,210 --> 00:06:08,890
Qiao.

108
00:06:09,530 --> 00:06:10,250
Listen to me.

109
00:06:10,250 --> 00:06:11,510
I don't want to hear it.

110
00:06:12,850 --> 00:06:14,130
I won't let you get caught up in the feud between the Duan family

111
00:06:14,130 --> 00:06:16,060
and the Sacred Blood Sect anymore.

112
00:06:16,090 --> 00:06:16,970
Of course not.

113
00:06:17,530 --> 00:06:18,450
If you kill me,

114
00:06:18,500 --> 00:06:20,030
I won't get involved at all.

115
00:06:20,330 --> 00:06:21,250
Gu Qingqiao.

116
00:06:21,610 --> 00:06:23,130
Can you let me finish?

117
00:06:23,130 --> 00:06:24,390
I don't want to hear it.

118
00:06:24,930 --> 00:06:26,250
Once I find the Four Treasures,

119
00:06:26,250 --> 00:06:27,850
I'll disappear completely.

120
00:06:27,850 --> 00:06:30,850
You won't have to go through the trouble of killing me.

121
00:06:31,140 --> 00:06:31,890
Qiao.

122
00:06:32,970 --> 00:06:34,100
What I meant to say is

123
00:06:34,530 --> 00:06:35,250
I found...

124
00:06:35,250 --> 00:06:36,180
Enough, Duan Yu.

125
00:06:36,570 --> 00:06:38,230
Don't make this harder for me.

126
00:06:38,890 --> 00:06:41,820
Let's leave some good memories between us.

127
00:06:41,970 --> 00:06:43,370
Isn't that better?

128
00:06:46,470 --> 00:06:48,530
There's something I want to give you,

129
00:06:48,690 --> 00:06:49,409
but

130
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:52,250
I only want to ask you one thing.

131
00:06:56,130 --> 00:06:57,010
I loved you.

132
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:11,600
Truly loved.

133
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:15,500
So bad.

134
00:07:15,530 --> 00:07:16,380
So bad.

135
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,750
So bad.

136
00:07:17,990 --> 00:07:19,010
So bad.

137
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:20,240
Why is he so bad?

138
00:07:20,270 --> 00:07:21,200
So bad.

139
00:07:22,500 --> 00:07:24,780
Qing, why didn't you tell me earlier?

140
00:07:24,890 --> 00:07:26,850
How could you let such a heartless man

141
00:07:26,850 --> 00:07:28,250
come here?

142
00:07:28,490 --> 00:07:30,460
That was a long time ago.

143
00:07:30,850 --> 00:07:31,450
Qing,

144
00:07:31,540 --> 00:07:32,270
don't worry.

145
00:07:32,290 --> 00:07:33,970
We will support you.

146
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:35,010
I agree.

147
00:07:36,110 --> 00:07:37,170
It's really unnecessary.

148
00:07:37,170 --> 00:07:38,220
I just hope

149
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:41,080
he recovers quickly and leaves the mountain soon.

150
00:07:41,780 --> 00:07:43,640
Leaves the mountain soon, right?

151
00:07:43,890 --> 00:07:44,530
Got it.

152
00:07:45,210 --> 00:07:48,210
I'll make sure he recovers quickly.

153
00:07:49,090 --> 00:07:50,460
Don't mess around.

154
00:07:50,570 --> 00:07:52,590
After all, he is the young master of Changqing's Duan family.

155
00:07:52,590 --> 00:07:53,830
Qing,

156
00:07:54,409 --> 00:07:56,330
don't worry.

157
00:08:02,650 --> 00:08:03,520
Does it hurt?

158
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,780
The dressing I gave you

159
00:08:04,810 --> 00:08:07,170
is the best in Xiling.

160
00:08:07,810 --> 00:08:09,290
It hurts a little.

161
00:08:10,090 --> 00:08:13,900
But as the young master of the Duan family,

162
00:08:14,250 --> 00:08:16,730
you should be able to endure it.

163
00:08:17,860 --> 00:08:19,850
Thank you, Miss Fu Rong.

164
00:08:19,850 --> 00:08:20,890
You're welcome.

165
00:08:22,770 --> 00:08:23,580
Thank you.

166
00:08:24,410 --> 00:08:26,410
I'll change the dressing tomorrow.

167
00:08:33,330 --> 00:08:33,970
Young Master.

168
00:08:33,970 --> 00:08:36,429
This medicine has a pain-relieving effect.

169
00:08:36,470 --> 00:08:37,799
I'll prepare it for you.

170
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:38,590
No need.

171
00:08:40,620 --> 00:08:42,950
Something is wrong with the dressing.

172
00:08:48,070 --> 00:08:50,030
Young Master, how is your arm?

173
00:08:52,470 --> 00:08:53,300
It's okay.

174
00:08:53,620 --> 00:08:56,650
It seems they don't want you to stay here.

175
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:58,900
Qiao has a misunderstanding about me,

176
00:08:58,900 --> 00:09:00,700
and they are hostile towards me.

177
00:09:00,830 --> 00:09:02,090
It's understandable.

178
00:09:03,890 --> 00:09:05,080
You like her

179
00:09:05,170 --> 00:09:06,200
but she doesn't.

180
00:09:06,290 --> 00:09:08,110
So what even if you can understand?

181
00:09:08,110 --> 00:09:09,080
Let's go.

182
00:09:09,210 --> 00:09:10,570
Let's heal your arm first.

183
00:09:10,570 --> 00:09:11,700
You can't leave yet.

184
00:09:12,140 --> 00:09:13,170
After careful thinking,

185
00:09:13,170 --> 00:09:15,210
Qiao is here for two reasons.

186
00:09:15,930 --> 00:09:19,090
One is that the Sacred Blood Sect disciples are here.

187
00:09:19,730 --> 00:09:20,970
-Sacred Blood Sect disciples?
-The second

188
00:09:20,970 --> 00:09:22,000
is that

189
00:09:22,850 --> 00:09:24,250
the Four Treasures are here.

190
00:09:24,250 --> 00:09:27,250
So, treating your arm is only an excuse for you to stay?

191
00:09:27,370 --> 00:09:29,930
Well, the romance writer

192
00:09:30,810 --> 00:09:31,830
got it right this time.

193
00:09:31,830 --> 00:09:32,630
Young Master.

194
00:09:33,050 --> 00:09:34,970
So you didn't tell Miss Gu

195
00:09:34,970 --> 00:09:36,250
about the necklace

196
00:09:36,250 --> 00:09:37,320
because

197
00:09:37,410 --> 00:09:40,000
you couldn't ensure her absolute safety,

198
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,290
right?

199
00:09:41,700 --> 00:09:43,570
If you did, the other three Treasures

200
00:09:43,570 --> 00:09:45,240
would fall into the hands of the Sacred Blood Sect.

201
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,510
But your arm...

202
00:09:46,850 --> 00:09:47,610
It's fine.

203
00:09:48,580 --> 00:09:50,310
We'll take it one step at a time.

204
00:09:50,450 --> 00:09:51,510
There will be a way.

205
00:09:57,010 --> 00:10:00,480
[Penglai Bathhouse]

206
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:04,560
Qing, are you alright?

207
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,770
Need any help?

208
00:10:06,230 --> 00:10:07,890
I'm just a little tired.

209
00:10:08,830 --> 00:10:10,260
I'll be fine with some rest.

210
00:10:10,260 --> 00:10:11,360
You all go on with your work.

211
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,480
Take care of yourself

212
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:13,610
and don't overwork.

213
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:17,550
Finally, we can reopen.

214
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:19,580
Miss Gu.

215
00:10:19,770 --> 00:10:20,900
What a coincidence!

216
00:10:26,530 --> 00:10:27,300
Qiao

217
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:28,380
Listen to me.

218
00:10:29,060 --> 00:10:30,740
Qiao, you misunderstood me.

219
00:10:30,810 --> 00:10:31,550
Qiao.

220
00:10:34,090 --> 00:10:34,910
Qiao.

221
00:10:35,010 --> 00:10:36,190
Let me explain.

222
00:10:36,250 --> 00:10:37,330
Make way.

223
00:10:58,990 --> 00:10:59,980
Miss Gu,

224
00:11:00,380 --> 00:11:02,380
Young Master is not good with words.

225
00:11:02,570 --> 00:11:04,630
He tends to bear everything himself,

226
00:11:04,830 --> 00:11:06,770
but I can't stand it anymore.

227
00:11:07,230 --> 00:11:08,450
The truth is, on that day,

228
00:11:08,450 --> 00:11:10,300
His Lordship ordered to kill you.

229
00:11:10,300 --> 00:11:13,110
Young Master had no choice but to go along with it.

230
00:11:13,290 --> 00:11:15,930
He never intended to deceive you.

231
00:11:16,670 --> 00:11:18,740
He was deceitful from the beginning,

232
00:11:18,890 --> 00:11:19,900
always testing me.

233
00:11:19,900 --> 00:11:24,470
[Dining Hall]

234
00:11:21,660 --> 00:11:24,380
He did intend to test you at first,

235
00:11:24,690 --> 00:11:26,350
but he quickly gave up on that.

236
00:11:26,370 --> 00:11:28,230
I've known him since we were kids,

237
00:11:28,250 --> 00:11:30,250
and I've never seen him act like this towards anyone.

238
00:11:30,250 --> 00:11:31,180
He'd rather have you hate him

239
00:11:31,180 --> 00:11:32,550
to protect you,

240
00:11:32,770 --> 00:11:34,010
afraid that His Lordship would realize

241
00:11:34,010 --> 00:11:35,470
his true feelings for you.

242
00:11:35,590 --> 00:11:37,660
He even planned a prison break for you.

243
00:11:37,660 --> 00:11:39,250
If it hadn't been for that Mantra cultist interfering...

244
00:11:39,250 --> 00:11:40,050
No!

245
00:11:40,250 --> 00:11:40,980
I'm the Star of Rebellion.

246
00:11:40,980 --> 00:11:42,250
I'll destroy the Duan family.

247
00:11:42,250 --> 00:11:43,580
Duan Yu wants to kill me.

248
00:11:44,820 --> 00:11:45,650
Miss Gu.

249
00:11:46,990 --> 00:11:55,360
[Dining Hall]

250
00:11:47,030 --> 00:11:47,840
Enough.

251
00:11:48,850 --> 00:11:50,810
We are destined to be enemies.

252
00:11:54,250 --> 00:11:55,440
Didn't you say

253
00:11:55,610 --> 00:11:57,850
that you will find a way

254
00:11:57,850 --> 00:11:59,460
to embrace both your faith and your beloved?

255
00:11:59,460 --> 00:12:01,220
If there really was such a way,

256
00:12:01,250 --> 00:12:02,150
Tsangyang Gyatso

257
00:12:02,150 --> 00:12:03,930
wouldn't have left the world so early.

258
00:12:03,930 --> 00:12:05,530
Who is Tsangyang Gyatso?

259
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:07,620
A lama who wrote romantic poetry.

260
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:09,530
What a talented poet.

261
00:12:11,060 --> 00:12:12,410
Can you write me a recommendation

262
00:12:12,410 --> 00:12:13,530
to visit him?

263
00:12:13,730 --> 00:12:16,650
Even if it's just to share a drink.

264
00:12:16,890 --> 00:12:18,700
It's not possible.

265
00:12:20,210 --> 00:12:21,490
You should leave here

266
00:12:22,170 --> 00:12:22,850
But...

267
00:12:23,490 --> 00:12:24,890
Young Master's injury...

268
00:12:24,890 --> 00:12:26,280
What injury?

269
00:12:26,330 --> 00:12:27,490
Fu Rong said

270
00:12:27,490 --> 00:12:28,890
he'll recover soon.

271
00:12:30,260 --> 00:12:32,610
It's not that easy to heal.

272
00:12:32,770 --> 00:12:33,540
Xing Si.

273
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,210
This is Xiling.

274
00:12:35,330 --> 00:12:36,790
Everyone here is a doctor.

275
00:12:36,950 --> 00:12:39,010
It's like faking illness at a university hospital.

276
00:12:39,010 --> 00:12:40,440
You can't fool the doctors,

277
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:41,890
only yourselves.

278
00:12:44,160 --> 00:12:45,290
Tell him that

279
00:12:45,690 --> 00:12:47,420
since he didn't come to kill me,

280
00:12:47,830 --> 00:12:49,090
I'm not angry anymore.

281
00:12:49,370 --> 00:12:53,630
[Dining Hall]

282
00:12:49,650 --> 00:12:51,650
We're just not meant to be together.

283
00:12:52,650 --> 00:12:54,210
It's best we go our separate ways,

284
00:12:54,210 --> 00:12:55,340
looking at each other from a distance.

285
00:12:55,340 --> 00:12:59,090
Is that also from Mr. Gyatso?

286
00:13:01,250 --> 00:13:02,710
That's from Mr. Chunjiao.

287
00:13:02,970 --> 00:13:04,700
There's a Mr. Chunjiao as well?

288
00:13:08,010 --> 00:13:09,290
