589
00:28:05,860 --> 00:28:07,300
Nothing.

590
00:28:07,610 --> 00:28:09,100
Feel free to continue your recovery.

591
00:28:09,100 --> 00:28:11,400
I'm tired today.

592
00:28:13,970 --> 00:28:17,210
