601
00:28:55,500 --> 00:28:56,660
A gold pot.

602
00:28:57,180 --> 00:28:58,940
Quite expensive.

603
00:29:02,130 --> 00:29:02,850
But

604
00:29:03,380 --> 00:29:05,710
