605
00:29:06,170 --> 00:29:08,730
Nothing interesting.

606
00:29:09,620 --> 00:29:10,380
Boring.

607
00:29:11,210 --> 00:29:11,930
Boring.

608
00:29:15,610 --> 00:29:19,210
There's something odd about Duan Yu

609
00:29:20,570 --> 00:29:22,660
