610
00:29:22,820 --> 00:29:27,740
[Xiling] [Martial Arts]

611
00:29:40,800 --> 00:29:52,300
[Xiling] [Martial Arts]

612
00:29:41,800 --> 00:29:42,700
Great Master.

613
00:29:51,250 --> 00:29:52,300
Great Master.

614
00:29:53,130 --> 00:29:54,170
