615
00:29:54,530 --> 00:29:56,370
They say your name is Pipa.

616
00:29:57,070 --> 00:29:57,860
Why?

617
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:00,540
Pipa is such a beautiful name.

618
00:30:01,220 --> 00:30:02,250
You...

