I'm not saying

626
00:30:15,530 --> 00:30:18,090
you're not good-looking.

627
00:30:18,700 --> 00:30:19,700
I'm saying

628
00:30:20,460 --> 00:30:22,290
you're ugly.

629
00:30:23,650 --> 00:30:24,610
Great Master,

630
00:30:25,610 --> 00:30:27,010
you should take a rest.

631
00:30:27,040 --> 00:30:28,100
I'll head back now.

632
00:30:32,350 --> 00:30:34,270
My arm hurts.

633
00:30:34,290 --> 00:30:35,510
I didn't touch you.

634
00:30:37,410 --> 00:30:39,810
Dong... something Chun?

635
00:30:41,340 --> 00:30:42,540
I think

636
00:30:42,730 --> 00:30:44,380
