646
00:31:11,890 --> 00:31:14,770
Why do they call you Pipa?

647
00:31:15,890 --> 00:31:17,580
A long, long time ago,

648
00:31:17,840 --> 00:31:19,630
I lived in a faraway place.

649
00:31:20,270 --> 00:31:22,270
Later, I came to Changqing,

650
00:31:22,770 --> 00:31:24,940
but my behavior was strange,

651
00:31:24,970 --> 00:31:26,520
and different from others.

652
00:31:27,050 --> 00:31:29,910
In my hometown, people like that are called 'Qipa,'

653
00:31:30,420 --> 00:31:31,660
but somehow

654
00:31:32,030 --> 00:31:34,270
they started calling me 'Pipa.'

655
00:31:36,010 --> 00:31:38,290
Does Duan Yu call you that too?

656
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:43,620
Sometimes.

657
00:31:43,890 --> 00:31:44,980
It seems

658
00:31:45,450 --> 00:31:49,580
