664
00:32:14,840 --> 00:32:15,580
Tell me.

665
00:32:16,210 --> 00:32:17,970
Why did you come to Xiling?

666
00:32:17,990 --> 00:32:18,610
I...

667
00:32:18,930 --> 00:32:20,960
I came to learn medicine.

668
00:32:20,980 --> 00:32:22,740
[Xiling] [Martial Arts]

669
00:32:22,850 --> 00:32:25,460
Do you believe I'll kill you?

670
00:32:25,810 --> 00:32:26,570
No, no.

671
00:32:27,320 --> 00:32:28,450
I'll tell the truth.

672
00:32:28,560 --> 00:32:29,930
I... I'll be honest.

673
00:32:44,790 --> 00:32:45,790
Great Master,

674
00:32:46,090 --> 00:32:48,080
I have a rare disease

675
00:32:48,340 --> 00:32:50,470
that only the Qingmu Sword can cure.

676
00:32:50,610 --> 00:32:52,230
If I don't find it,

677
00:32:52,450 --> 00:32:53,250
I'll die.

678
00:32:53,620 --> 00:32:56,730
Did you plan this with Duan Yu?

679
00:32:57,470 --> 00:32:58,250
No.

680
00:32:58,520 --> 00:32:59,840
