685
00:33:08,050 --> 00:33:09,370
He agreed?

686
00:33:10,650 --> 00:33:11,850
I don't believe you.

687
00:33:19,970 --> 00:33:21,090
Here,

688
00:33:21,850 --> 00:33:23,330
