689
00:33:23,810 --> 00:33:25,170
Let me see.

690
00:33:26,770 --> 00:33:28,250
Let me see.

691
00:33:32,920 --> 00:33:33,450
You...

692
00:33:33,820 --> 00:33:35,220
You broke the agreement.

693
00:33:35,250 --> 00:33:37,710
It's written in black and white.

694
00:33:37,740 --> 00:33:38,300
You...

695
00:33:38,370 --> 00:33:40,030
You're not keeping your word.

696
00:33:41,130 --> 00:33:41,890
I...

697
00:33:42,140 --> 00:33:44,100
I'm not keeping my word.

698
00:33:44,140 --> 00:33:45,120
So what?

699
00:33:45,450 --> 00:33:47,120
If you don't like it, fight me!

700
00:33:47,140 --> 00:33:47,690
I...

701
00:33:48,440 --> 00:33:49,670
You little brat,

702
00:33:50,110 --> 00:33:51,350
