703
00:33:51,430 --> 00:33:52,330
I'll hit you

704
00:33:52,350 --> 00:33:53,510
again.

705
00:33:55,630 --> 00:33:57,900
Dong something Chun?

706
00:33:58,010 --> 00:33:59,420
Dongfangchun Jiaoqing

707
00:33:59,470 --> 00:34:00,790
I'm telling you.

708
00:34:01,480 --> 00:34:02,730
I won't give you

709
00:34:02,760 --> 00:34:04,760
the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword.

710
00:34:05,050 --> 00:34:06,680
If you want to live,

711
00:34:06,780 --> 00:34:10,650
you better cook me braised pork every day.

712
00:34:16,500 --> 00:34:17,860
All you do

713
00:34:17,900 --> 00:34:19,250
is eat.

714
00:34:19,270 --> 00:34:20,560
You even eat paper!

715
00:34:19,739 --> 00:34:21,320
[Xiling]

716
00:34:22,530 --> 00:34:23,620
What should I do?

717
00:34:23,860 --> 00:34:25,790
My Black Wood Human-shaped Sword.

718
00:34:28,850 --> 00:34:29,489
Siqiong,

719
00:34:30,739 --> 00:34:32,460
can you tell me

720
00:34:33,389 --> 00:34:36,190
