724
00:34:44,760 --> 00:34:46,610
I am destined to help her draw the sword.

725
00:34:46,610 --> 00:34:50,040
The guardian only draws the sword for those who are worthy.

726
00:34:50,760 --> 00:34:53,500
That child lacks the wisdom

727
00:34:53,810 --> 00:34:55,210
and spirit

728
00:34:55,570 --> 00:34:57,650
to take on such a great responsibility.

729
00:34:57,650 --> 00:34:58,330
Qing.

730
00:34:58,460 --> 00:34:58,970
Qing...

731
00:34:58,970 --> 00:34:59,770
Stop it.

732
00:35:01,140 --> 00:35:03,580
I will not risk your life

733
00:35:03,610 --> 00:35:06,650
for an uncertain future.

734
00:35:07,530 --> 00:35:08,410
Master,

735
00:35:09,350 --> 00:35:10,960
the first time I saw her,

736
00:35:11,490 --> 00:35:13,020
she reminded me of someone.

737
00:35:13,050 --> 00:35:13,640
No.

738
00:35:13,690 --> 00:35:14,340
Yes.

739
00:35:14,670 --> 00:35:17,130
The first time I saw her, my heart fluttered.

740
00:35:17,290 --> 00:35:19,560
Because she resembles Shan Yao so much.

741
00:35:19,660 --> 00:35:20,610
No.

742
00:35:20,900 --> 00:35:22,700
It's because she's the sword seeker.

743
00:35:22,700 --> 00:35:24,370
That's why you felt that way.

744
00:35:26,550 --> 00:35:27,350
So,

745
00:35:29,270 --> 00:35:31,000
she really is the sword seeker.

746
00:35:33,210 --> 00:35:34,580
Leave me alone for a while.

747
00:35:34,580 --> 00:35:36,490
I need to think.

748
00:35:39,830 --> 00:35:41,180
Try this.

749
00:35:42,640 --> 00:35:44,170
Resemble? This is rubbish!

750
00:35:45,120 --> 00:35:45,830
Master.

751
00:35:46,620 --> 00:35:47,410
I was wrong.

752
00:35:47,430 --> 00:35:48,490
I'm sorry.

753
00:35:49,280 --> 00:35:50,340
Just eat.

754
00:35:50,880 --> 00:35:51,590
Okay.

755
00:35:57,180 --> 00:35:59,430
Master, I'm full.

756
00:36:03,130 --> 00:36:04,540
-Master, did you finish your meal?
-Master.

757
00:36:04,540 --> 00:36:05,860
Rubbish!

758
00:36:11,410 --> 00:36:12,450
Junior,

759
00:36:12,950 --> 00:36:15,080
