760
00:36:15,160 --> 00:36:15,770
No.

761
00:36:17,240 --> 00:36:18,970
He's treating us differently!

762
00:36:19,300 --> 00:36:20,460
It's so unfair.

763
00:36:20,900 --> 00:36:22,230
I'm hurt.

764
00:36:26,970 --> 00:36:27,570
Senior.

765
00:36:27,880 --> 00:36:29,200
If I'm not around,

766
00:36:29,660 --> 00:36:31,190
