767
00:36:31,470 --> 00:36:33,420
I can't be alone with him.

768
00:36:34,310 --> 00:36:35,920
Look, it's only been a few days

769
00:36:35,920 --> 00:36:36,600
and

770
00:36:37,880 --> 00:36:39,650
I already have a few more wrinkles.

771
00:36:39,650 --> 00:36:40,560
Senior.

772
00:36:40,730 --> 00:36:42,860
Master actually cares about you a lot.

773
00:36:43,100 --> 00:36:45,030
He just doesn't know how to show it.

774
00:36:45,690 --> 00:36:47,690
He seems to know how to show it to you!

775
00:36:50,060 --> 00:36:50,750
By the way,

776
00:36:51,330 --> 00:36:52,260
a few days ago,

777
00:36:52,610 --> 00:36:53,810
you promised me

778
00:36:53,970 --> 00:36:57,130
you'd help me train the next generation of Xiling talents.

779
00:36:57,130 --> 00:36:57,730
How can you

780
00:36:57,980 --> 00:36:59,170
go back on your word

781
00:36:59,570 --> 00:37:00,890
so soon?

782
00:37:00,990 --> 00:37:02,720
The moon waxes and wanes.

783
00:37:03,330 --> 00:37:04,770
People come and go.

784
00:37:05,130 --> 00:37:07,050
Change is the only constant.

785
00:37:07,200 --> 00:37:10,220
Xiling is getting weaker.

786
00:37:11,250 --> 00:37:12,250
If you leave,

787
00:37:12,560 --> 00:37:14,320
we'll be even more vulnerable.

788
00:37:16,990 --> 00:37:18,830
Master's always angry with you

789
00:37:19,180 --> 00:37:21,450
because he's worried about this too.

790
00:37:21,780 --> 00:37:22,980
If fate is against me,

791
00:37:23,530 --> 00:37:25,050
what can I do?

792
00:37:25,250 --> 00:37:26,500
Senior,

793
00:37:26,970 --> 00:37:28,770
you're destined for greatness.

794
00:37:28,770 --> 00:37:30,170
Heaven will protect you.

795
00:37:30,410 --> 00:37:31,250
Heaven?

796
00:37:31,930 --> 00:37:33,390
Even you don't protect me!

797
00:37:33,750 --> 00:37:35,150
You're such a swindler.

798
00:37:35,650 --> 00:37:36,650
swindler?

799
00:37:41,390 --> 00:37:43,190
That's what Qing said, isn't it?

800
00:37:45,250 --> 00:37:46,060
Yes.

801
00:37:46,420 --> 00:37:47,500
Qing,

802
00:37:47,530 --> 00:37:49,650
has been here for a long time,

803
00:37:50,260 --> 00:37:52,120
helping with the medicinal baths

804
00:37:52,310 --> 00:37:54,840
and encouraging the Xiling disciples.

805
00:37:55,170 --> 00:37:58,090
She might not be the brightest student,

806
00:37:58,200 --> 00:37:59,440
but she's a good person.

807
00:37:59,440 --> 00:38:00,610
