808
00:38:01,930 --> 00:38:04,890
she could stay longer

809
00:38:05,370 --> 00:38:07,690
and help us more.

810
00:38:07,960 --> 00:38:08,840
Yeah,

811
00:38:10,080 --> 00:38:12,200
but I won't see her for a long time.

812
00:38:12,310 --> 00:38:15,190
So, you shouldn't leave.

813
00:38:17,760 --> 00:38:19,200
I don't want to, either.

814
00:38:25,050 --> 00:38:27,370
What do you think I'm doing here?

815
00:38:31,080 --> 00:38:31,890
I'm waiting for you.

816
00:38:31,890 --> 00:38:33,700
How did you know I would come?

817
00:38:33,960 --> 00:38:35,480
Ever since you came here,

818
00:38:35,970 --> 00:38:37,740
I've felt your presence.

819
00:38:38,500 --> 00:38:41,780
I feel your gaze on me every moment.

820
00:38:43,970 --> 00:38:45,410
Xing Si told me

821
00:38:46,630 --> 00:38:48,950
that you weren't trying to kill me,

822
00:38:49,850 --> 00:38:51,280
but to protect me.

823
00:38:51,690 --> 00:38:54,010
I told him I wasn't angry anymore.

824
00:38:54,810 --> 00:38:56,820
Those words weren't for him.

825
00:38:57,120 --> 00:38:58,250
They were for you.

826
00:38:58,540 --> 00:38:59,590
Qiao.

827
00:38:59,620 --> 00:39:00,850
Do you really forgive me?

828
00:39:00,850 --> 00:39:03,370
Actually, on the way back to Xiling,

829
00:39:03,600 --> 00:39:04,860
I already forgave you.

830
00:39:06,250 --> 00:39:07,710
Quickly pack your things.

831
00:39:07,950 --> 00:39:09,280
Let's go back to Changqing.

832
00:39:09,280 --> 00:39:10,130
Look at you.

833
00:39:10,380 --> 00:39:12,220
The calm and composed Young Master Duan

834
00:39:12,220 --> 00:39:13,810
