835
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:14,930
Don't interrupt.

836
00:39:14,970 --> 00:39:17,100
It doesn't matter whether I'm acting crazy or not.

837
00:39:17,100 --> 00:39:18,100
What's important

838
00:39:18,440 --> 00:39:19,510
is that you come with me.

839
00:39:19,510 --> 00:39:20,480
Young Master Duan.

840
00:39:20,480 --> 00:39:21,870
Do you think

841
00:39:22,090 --> 00:39:23,250
I was joking

842
00:39:23,520 --> 00:39:24,780
when I said we should

843
00:39:25,230 --> 00:39:26,470
go our separate ways?

844
00:39:27,030 --> 00:39:29,010
Since I learned about the ancient feud

845
00:39:29,010 --> 00:39:30,950
between the Star of Rebellion and the Duan family,

846
00:39:30,950 --> 00:39:31,870
I knew

847
00:39:32,870 --> 00:39:35,520
we could never be together.

848
00:39:36,280 --> 00:39:37,750
Since I came to Xiling,

849
00:39:38,150 --> 00:39:39,790
I've been lying to myself,

850
00:39:40,610 --> 00:39:42,170
telling myself

851
00:39:42,370 --> 00:39:44,530
that even if I can't find the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword,

852
00:39:44,530 --> 00:39:48,020
it's good enough to stay here in this peaceful land.

853
00:39:48,090 --> 00:39:50,550
So, you've been focusing on medicinal baths

854
00:39:51,030 --> 00:39:52,620
and learning medicine.

855
00:39:53,170 --> 00:39:53,880
Yes.

856
00:39:54,270 --> 00:39:56,010
But the changing color of the flower petals

857
00:39:56,010 --> 00:39:57,540
reminds me

858
00:39:57,540 --> 00:39:59,960
that I must find the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword.

859
00:39:59,960 --> 00:40:02,070
Even if I find it,

860
00:40:03,090 --> 00:40:05,820
there are still two things left unaccounted for.

861
00:40:05,930 --> 00:40:07,170
I've accepted my fate.

862
00:40:07,170 --> 00:40:07,930
Qiao.

863
00:40:08,250 --> 00:40:08,550
Actually...

864
00:40:08,550 --> 00:40:09,120
Duan Yu.

865
00:40:09,120 --> 00:40:09,530
I...

866
00:40:09,930 --> 00:40:11,580
It took me

867
00:40:13,010 --> 00:40:15,470
a lot of courage to tell you this.

